item.description:
Please join the Rhode Island Atheist Society at our first potluck dinner! Come for good food, a glass of cheer, and as always, terrific debates and discussions.

If you are able to attend please let us know what you would like to bring. I'll email my address to those attending a few days prior to the event. If you have any questions please don't hesitate to contact me.

Hope to see you there!
item.name: Rhode Island Atheist Society - Potluck Dinner - October 22, 2010
